data.description: A perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality.  With newer upgrades including a roof, AC system, impact windows, doors, French doors, updated bathroom, kitchen cabinets, countertops, you can enjoy modern amenities in a homey atmosphere. The high ceilings, wood-burning fireplace, and tile flooring create a cozy ambiance in the multiple living areas. The primary suite features a sitting area, open closet, and spacious bathroom with a walk-in shower and separate tub. The split floor plan ensures sufficient privacy between bedrooms. The expansive screened-in patio overlooks a refreshing pool, perfect for hosting guests. This house is situated in a superb location, providing the perfect blend of privacy and proximity to a variety of amenities such as schools, shops, dining options, and exciting attractions like Disney, beaches, cruise ships, and rocket launches!
